lead_paragraph: The House speaker defeated a political newcomer who had received a late surge of attention after being praised by Donald J. Trump.

headline.print_headline: Ryan Routs Challenger Given Lift by Trump
headline.main: Paul Ryan Wins Republican Primary in Wisconsin

snippet: The House speaker defeated a political newcomer who had received a late surge of attention after being praised by Donald J. Trump....
abstract: House Speaker Paul D Ryan wins Wisconsin's Republican primary in landslide, defeating rival Paul Nehlen with 84 percent of vote.
